&lt;span class="date"&gt;&lt;a href="/search?l=blink-dev@chromium.org&amp;q=date:20241127" rel="nofollow"&gt;Wed, 27 Nov 2024 11:12:32 -0800&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
